cast.overview: The adventures of a group of Texas teens on their last day of school in 1976, centering on student Randall Floyd, who moves easily among stoners, jocks and geeks. Floyd is a star athlete, but he also likes smoking weed, which presents a conundrum when his football coach demands he sign a "no drugs" pledge.
cast.title: Dazed and Confused

details.biography: Christin Hinojosa (born October 3, 1975) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Sabrina in the 1993 film Dazed and Confused. After a few other small roles in films and on television, Hinojosa left acting in the late 1990s. She holds a master's degree in social work from the University Chicago, and has worked in non-profits for the majority of her career.
details.name: Christin Hinojosa
